| Exception               | Raised When...                                     |
| ----------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **`ZeroDivisionError`** | You divide by zero.                                |
| **`ValueError`**        | Invalid value (e.g., converting `"abc"` to `int`). |
| **`TypeError`**         | Operation on wrong data type (e.g., `"2" + 2`).    |
| **`IndexError`**        | Index out of range in a list.                      |
| **`KeyError`**          | Dictionary key not found.                          |
| **`NameError`**         | Variable not defined.                              |
| **`FileNotFoundError`** | File doesnâ€™t exist when trying to open it.         |
| **`AttributeError`**    | Invalid attribute access.                          |
| **`ImportError`**       | Import fails.                                      |
| **`RuntimeError`**      | Generic runtime error.                             |
| **`StopIteration`**     | Raised by `next()` on an exhausted iterator.       |
